GeneralExplanation.ReturnReference: Form 990, Part VI, Line 12c: Explanation of Monitoring and Enforcement of Conflicts
GeneralExplanation.Explanation: A LIST OF ALL OFFICERS, DIRECTORS OR TRUSTEES AND KEY EMPLOYEES IS COMPILED AT THE END OF THE FISCAL YEAR. CONFLICT OF INTEREST REQUEST FORMS ARE DELIVERED TO EACH PERSON ON THE LIST. RESPONSES ARE COMPILED AND REVIEWED AND PRESENTED TO MANAGEMENT.

GeneralExplanation.ReturnReference: Form 990, Part VI, Line 11: Form 990 Review Process
GeneralExplanation.Explanation: A COPY OF THE FORM 990 IS PROVIDED TO THE DIRECTORS BEFORE FILING

GeneralExplanation.ReturnReference: Form 990, Part VI, Line 7a: How Members or Shareholders Elect Governing Body
GeneralExplanation.Explanation: Each year at their annual meeting, the directors elect replacements for those directors whose terms are expiring. Election of directors is subject to ratification by TAMC.
